import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useParams } from "react-router-dom"; import { format} from "date-fns"; const FieldDetails = () => { const { ticketId } = useParams(); const [ticketDetails, setticketDetails] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { if (ticketId) { fetch(`/api/ticket/${ticketId}`) .then((response) => response.json()) .then((data) => setticketDetails(data)) .catch((error) => console.error("Error fetching ticket details:", error) ); } }, [ticketId]); if (!ticketDetails) { return
Loading...
; } console.log(ticketDetails); return ( <>

Ticket Number: {ticketDetails.reference}

Reference: {ticketDetails.reference ? ticketDetails.reference : "Non rempli"}

Status:

{ticketDetails.status ? ticketDetails.status : "Non rempli"}

Service station:

{ticketDetails.service_station ? ticketDetails.service_station : "Non rempli"}

Client:

{ticketDetails.client?.client ? ticketDetails.client?.client : "Non rempli"}

Equipement S/N:

{ticketDetails.status ? ticketDetails.status : "Non rempli"}

Service type:

{ticketDetails.service_type ? ticketDetails.service_type : "Non rempli"}

TYPE:

{ticketDetails.type ? ticketDetails.type : "Non rempli"}

Call Time :

{ticketDetails.call_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.call_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

Receiving Time:

{ticketDetails.receiving_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.receiving_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

Technicien:

{ticketDetails.technicien ? ( <> {ticketDetails.technicien.firstname || ''} {ticketDetails.technicien.lastname || ''} ) : ( "N/A" )}

Contact:

{ticketDetails.contact ? ( <> {ticketDetails.contact.name || ''} | {ticketDetails.contact.email || ''} | {ticketDetails.contact.mobile || ''} ) : ( "N/A" )}

Accepting time:

{ticketDetails.accepting_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.accepting_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

Starting time:

{ticketDetails.starting_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.starting_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

Solving time:

{ticketDetails.solving_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.solving_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

Completion time:

{ticketDetails.solving_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.solving_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

Solving time:

{ticketDetails.solving_time ? format(new Date(ticketDetails.solving_time), 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:MM') : 'Not yet'}

) } export default FieldDetails
